    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1964-07-31T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1964-07-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="192"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d192">
                <head>192. Telegram From the Station in the Congo to the Central Intelligence
                        Agency<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d192fn1">Source: Central
                        Intelligence Agency Files, [<hi rend="italic">text not declassified</hi>],
                        Fiche 37, Row 5, Frames 2–3, [<hi rend="italic">text not declassified</hi>].
                        Secret; Immediate. Received at 1805Z.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Leopoldville</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1964-07-31">July 31, 1964</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2163 (In 40340). 1. [former <gloss target="#t_COS_1">COS</gloss>] has met with
                        [<persName corresp="#p_IDE_1">Identity 1</persName>], [<persName
                        corresp="#p_IDE_1">Identity 2</persName>], [<persName corresp="#p_IDE_1"
                        >Identity 3</persName>], [<hi rend="italic">1 line not declassified</hi>]
                        [<persName corresp="#p_MJD_1">Mobutu</persName>], [<persName
                        corresp="#p_IDE_1">Identity 4</persName>], [<hi rend="italic">name not
                        declassified</hi>], and [<persName corresp="#p_IDE_1">Identity
                    5</persName>]. All meetings went extremely well. Sending detailed cables 1 Aug
                    on each meeting.<note n="2" xml:id="d192fn2">See <ref target="#d194">Document
                            194</ref>.</note> [<hi rend="italic">name not declassified</hi>] present
                    for [<persName corresp="#p_IDE_1">Identity 5</persName>] meeting and [<gloss
                        target="#t_COS_1">COS</gloss>] present at numerous meetings with [<persName
                        corresp="#p_IDE_1">Identity 3</persName>] and [<persName corresp="#p_MJD_1"
                        >Mobutu</persName>] and [<persName corresp="#p_IDE_1">Identity 1</persName>]
                        [<hi rend="italic">cryptonym not declassified</hi>]</p>
                <p>2. [<hi rend="italic">5 lines not declassified</hi>] Full details 1 Aug.</p>
                <p>[<hi rend="italic">4 paragraphs (25 lines) not declassified</hi>]</p>
            </div>
        </body>
